            <title>[HTTPCLIENT-57] Define and implement Logging policy</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HTTPCLIENT-57</link>
                <project id="12310360" key="HTTPCLIENT">HttpComponents HttpClient</project>
                        <description>When to use info vs debug vs warning?  &lt;br/&gt;
When to log exceptions?&lt;br/&gt;
enter() and exit() messages on a per method basis?&lt;br/&gt;
Always log debug when swallowing an exception?</description>
